ementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7d9e2b0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Accurate lead qualification is a hallmark of Pardot. By employing sophisticated scoring and grading mechanisms, it helps in segregating quality leads from the rest. This accuracy in lead qualification is indispensable for crafting targeted marketing strategies and ensuring a higher conversion rate.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-059629e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"059629e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Improved Lead Segmentation<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93ef6ce elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"93ef6ce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce Pardot&#8217;s advanced lead segmentation capabilities allow for the creation of segmented lists based on various criteria. This segmentation is instrumental in delivering personalized messaging to different segments of the audience, thus elevating the effectiveness of marketing campaigns.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc2a8cd all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fc2a8c